title: Herbed Tofu Strength Roast — Clean Low-Carb Fuel 1
hydrationTip: Pair with 300–500 ml water for clean low-carb digestion.
method: Drain tofu and cut into cubes.
Heat olive oil in a pan and lightly brown tofu.
Add vegetables and cook until softened.
Season with herbs and salt.
Divide into four containers for batch prep.
swaps: Use tamari instead of herb blend for a savoury finish.
